Bxe2 Nh5 10. g3 O-O 11. Qd2 f5 12. O-O-O ({Another idea of Botvinnink was seen
in the following game:} 12. exf5 gxf5 13. O-O-O Bd7 14. f4 Be8 15. Rdf1 e4 $2 {
[%csl Re4,Rf5]} 16. g4 $1 Nf6 17. gxf5 Bd7 18. Rhg1 Bxf5 19. Rg5 Qd7 20. Rfg1
